## Attribution

This project includes the following components:

**Original Work (Daniel Kr채henb체hl - Hamilton Medical AG):**
- claude-safe.sh - Wrapper script for safe execution
- setup.sh - Installation and setup script
- docker-compose.yml - Container orchestration configuration
- README.md, QUICKSTART.md, CONTRIBUTORS.md - Documentation
- .gitignore, .env.example - Configuration templates

**Derived from Claude Code by Anthropic:**
- Dockerfile - Container image definition (from .devcontainer)
- devcontainer.json - VS Code Dev Container configuration
- init-firewall.sh - Network firewall script

The original Claude Code repository can be found at:
https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code

This project modifies and extends the original .devcontainer setup to provide
a standalone, secure Docker environment for running Claude Code with skip-permissions.
